In [98]:
for i in range(len(x)):
    fname = 'grras_img'+str(i)+".jpg"
    page = requests.get(x[i])
    if page.status_code == 200 and b'\\x' in page.content : 
        with open(fname,'wb') as fp:
            fp.write(page.content)
            fp.close()
        plt.imshow(plt.imread(fname))
        plt.xticks([])
        plt.yticks([])
        plt.show()
